difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.name=Animal Sickness Behavior
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.desc=Determines how animals react to sickness;
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.name.0=None
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.name.1=Vanilla
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.name.2=Renewed
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.desc.0=animals will never become sick.
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.desc.1=when sick, animals can not breed or drop any loot.
difficulty.parameter.AnimalSicknessBehavior.desc.2=when sick, animals can not breed, drop any loot, and will slowly die.
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.name=Crop Sickness Behavior
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.desc=Determines how crops react to sickness;
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.name.0=None
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.name.1=Vanilla
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.name.2=Renewed
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.desc.0=crops will never become sick.
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.desc.1=sick crops slowly spread disease to other crops, and will eventually die.
difficulty.parameter.CropSicknessBehavior.desc.2=sick crops scatter disease in a radius when they are harvested sick, or when they die.
difficulty.parameter.ChickenBreedingItem.name=Chicken Breeding Item
difficulty.parameter.ChickenBreedingItem.desc=What breeding item chickens use;
