difficulty.parameter.ChickenBreedingItem.name.1=Worms
difficulty.parameter.ChickenBreedingItem.desc.0=chickens will breed using seeds.
difficulty.parameter.ChickenBreedingItem.desc.1=chickens will breed using worms.

